text: Yevhen Serhiyovych Deidei (; 12 July 1987) was a Ukrainian politician. He was a member of the battalion of the Special Tasks Patrol Police "Kyiv-1". He was a People's Deputy of Ukraine from November 2014 until August 2019. In 2012 he was sentenced to five years in prison for robbery but was later released. ==References== Category:1987 births Category:2022 deaths Category:Members of the Verkhovna Rada Category:Ukrainian military people Category:Odesa Oblast
